title: PM chairs 1/2015 meeting of National Committee for Sustainable Development (Royal Thai Government)
text: ( Source : Royal Thai Government ) Prime Minister presided over the meeting of the National Committee for Sustainable Development to mobilize implementations according to the UN's Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) in a tangible manner.
